race.comment: ISHIKAWA LASS (7) comes off a big run when second in a handy 22.07 at this track over 390m. This is tougher but expected to be in the finish. ASTON SCANNER (6) followed a minor placing at Warragul two runs ago with a sound third, beaten 1.5 lengths, last start in a Mix 6/7 H at this track over 390m (22.11). In good form and in the mix. DASHING DONNA (9) resumed last time over 390m at this track and finished fifth (22.29) in a Mix 6/7 H. Has ability and can run well. Something for the Multiples: BLANKET GAME (4)
